"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/452396","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-02-23","<p>I met the National Chairman of the Defence Police Federation on 17 December 2015 to review the status of the ongoing negotiations on changes to Ministry of Defence Police terms and conditions of service. I would expect any issues associated with the morale of the Force to be raised and discussed at the Ministry of Defence Police Joint Consultative Committee that is chaired by the Chief Constable.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster",,"2016-02-23T15:28:18.03Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/452396/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/452396/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/452396/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-02-11","Ministry of Defence Police","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, if he will hold discussions with the Defence Police Federation on the (a) level of morale and (b) terms and conditions of service within the Ministry of Defence Police; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Mrs Madeleine Moon","Bridgend","Mrs Madeleine Moon","27065"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/452397","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-02-22","<p>Discussions between officials in the Ministry of Defence and the Department for Media, Culture and Sport will continue and an announcement with regard to the future of Victory 1744 will be made once these deliberations are complete.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster",,"2016-02-22T16:28:33.767Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/452397/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/452397/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/452397/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-02-11","HMS Victory","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, when he plans to inform the hon. Member for East Worthing and Shoreham of progress made on matters relating to the future of the Victory 1744 discussed in that hon. Member's meeting with the Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State for Defence in September 2015.","false","Biography information for Tim Loughton","East Worthing and Shoreham","Tim Loughton","27079"
